OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWinds easing
OL,6,Finland this evening then mostly clear
OL,7,Fovernight, with a few isolated mist
OL,8,Fand fog patches perhaps developing
OL,9,Ftowards dawn. Some low cloud affecting
OL,10,Fmore northeastern areas later in the
OL,11,Fnight. Becoming chilly with an
OL,12,Fisolated rural frost.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FAny low cloud and isolated
OL,15,Fmist and fog soon clearing to give
OL,16,Fanother fine and dry day with long
OL,17,Fsunny spells. Mild for most, but
OL,18,Fcooler towards the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
